            <h1>Hi, I'm Ruby Gould!</h1>
            <p class="tagline">Senior Product Designer</p>
            <div class="bio">
                <p>I'm a Product Designer and winter person who loves to get outside and touch grass! [cite: 1]</p>
                <p>Currently, I am on contract at <strong>Google</strong> as a Senior Product Designer on the <strong>Search Trust</strong> team, where I lead 0-1 design efforts for location experiences across Search and AI Mode[cite: 2, 6]. I specialize in advanced prototyping and design mentorship[cite: 3].</p>
